  <image class='logo' src='http://image.potatofield.cn/18-11-21/86474431.jpg'></image>
</view>
<view class='container'>
  <view class='title'>
    <text>请选择模式</text>
  </view>
</view>
<view class='container'>
  <button class='block-button' bindtap='multipleMode'>
    <view class='container row-flex'>
      <image class='half' mode='widthFix' src='http://image.potatofield.cn/18-11-24/74898333.jpg'></image>
      <view class='half content'>
        <text>输入号码范围和抽奖人数，一次性随机抽取获奖者</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='button-mask' hover-class='button-mask__hover'></view>
  </button>
</view>
<view class='container'>
  <button class='block-button' bindtap='singleMode'>
    <view class='container row-flex'>
      <image class='half' mode='widthFix' src='http://image.potatofield.cn/18-11-24/69411768.jpg'></image>
      <view class='half content'>
        <text>输入号码范围和抽签次数，每次随机抽取一个号码</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='button-mask' hover-class='button-mask__hover'></view>
  </button>
</view>
